I tryed some Bertoxxulous human casters at a time - when i stoped playing my human warrior, I had an enchanter on FV who followed Bertoxxulous, though i tested out a wizard, Mage and enchanter before.. all are fun fun choices.<br>
<br>
I think the best thing i found was mage pets can root before they engage in melee if the spell has refreshed. just /pet attack then /pet back off, i used to nuke until the root broke then had pet attack it again. (save on pet dieng)<br>
<br>
There is an really really nice quest you can buy all the components for - a finely crafted antique ring? i think with mana preservation 2 as an effect. Some people sell it in the bazaar for a few thousand plat but with PoK ports you can buy one for a few plat if you buy the components *grins*.<br>
<br>
And i contributed no usefull info - other than Magicians are great fun to have around, especially in your group.<br>
